</P>
<P>
 Children's singer Dave Kinnoin and other performers are on the menu with food 
from nearly 30 local restaurants at Brea Fest on Friday, Aug. 26, from 7 to 
10:30 p.m. at the Brea Civic & Cultural Center, 1 Civic Center Circle. Free 
admission; food "taste" tickets, $2 each. (714) 990-7735. 
</P>
