preschooler-parent workshop today, Aug. 25, at 2 p.m. and Saturday, Aug. 27, at 
10 a.m. at the Fullerton Arboretum, 1900 Associated Road. $7.50 per child, 
adults free. Reservations required. (714) 630-0519. 
</P>
