has not been charged in the incident because CHP officials believe Avetisyan's 
car "did not have any lights on or anything to forewarn motorists," Obregon 
said. 
</P>
<P>
 A male passenger in Avetisyan's car was questioned at the scene by CHP 
officers. Officials said the passenger, whose name was not released, apparently 
had consumed alcohol, but it was not known whether the dead man had been 
drinking. 
