<DOCNO> LA082594-0343 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 073100 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
August 25, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 1; Column 2; Entertainment Desk 
