17.5 17.5 4 Portugal 16 -- -- -- -- 16 15 Spain 15 -- -- -- -- 15 14 Sweden 25 
25 25 25 25 25 3 Source: Travelex Financial Services. Status as of March, 1994. 
</P>
<P>
 * 50% recoverable 
</P>
