<TEXT>
<P>
 Regarding: "Saving Blue Book From Ultimate Snub," Jeannine Stein, Aug. 18: 
</P>
<P>
 Apparently Ms. Allegra Yust has spent too many hours sipping tea in her 
mother's spacious, perfumed apartment. Is she really this naive, or was she, 
perhaps, abroad during the Los Angeles riots? 
</P>
